## Limitations

The analysis is limited by the availability of online resources and the potential bias in sources that focus predominantly on Western fashion trends. Additionally, the rapid pace of fashion changes in recent years may not be fully captured in historical analyses, and the impact of digital media on fashion trends is an emerging area that requires further exploration.

